          "slidetitle": "Introduction: AI Menus Explained",
          "subtitle": "What AI menus are and do",
          "slidecontent": "• AI-generated menus use algorithms to suggest dishes, ingredients, or full meal plans automatically\n• Common in apps, kiosks, and online ordering platforms\n• These systems learn from data like popular choices, seasonal availability, and customer preferences\n• No human chef reviewing every suggestion\n• Recommendations can change rapidly based on inputs\n• Crucially, AI does not always account for individual dietary needs or allergen risks"
