        {
          "number": 8,
          "slidetitle": "Key Points to Remember",
          "subtitle": "Essential reminders for safe AI menus",
          "slidecontent": "• Always verify AI-generated menus against confirmed ingredient lists before serving guests\n• Allergen errors can be life-threatening\n• Never rely solely on AI output when a guest declares a serious food allergy or intolerance\n• Cross-check AI recommendations with your kitchen team and current supplier information\n• Keep human oversight at every stage of the menu planning process\n• As a next step, review your current allergen protocols and identify where AI tools fit safely within them"
